[b]Update: v0.11.44 is out[/b] — the big fix release. Weekly goals got a full redesign (they now target specific open bundle slots, so no more impossible or already-donated asks), remixed bundles are fully supported (some were silently skipped before — that's also why remixed is the recommended setup), loop resets got an audit so nothing leaks between runs anymore (museum, gear, even max HP — and your clothes survive now), kept buildings rebuild where you placed them, green rain works in summer, and Better Chests/Unlimited Storage play nice with the stash.

Balance pass is next — the "beat it first try" crowd has been heard.

Nexus: [url]https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/47192[/url]
